steps.name: That I am logged into Axle

elements.name: Create a new order for customer

steps.name: I click the customers menu option
I search for a customer called "MercyAscot"
I view the customer called "MercyAscot"
I verify the customer name "MercyAscot" in working on info
I verify the empty cart
I click New Order button in user "MercyAscot" detail page
I verify the cart info for customer "MercyAscot"
I verify the initialized cart
I search for a product called "Yellow Gold Listing"
I view the product "Yellow Gold Listing"
I verify the product title "Yellow Gold Listing"
I verify the product sub-title "Yellow Digital Listings > Yellow digital listing products"

arguments.val: Yellow Digital Listings > Yellow digital listing products

steps.name: I verify the product meta info:
I add the product to cart
I verify the order stage texts:
I verify the current stage as "Item Details"
I verify the cart info for customer "MercyAscot"
I verify the base price of product "$110.00"
I have hidden the side bar
I select a category of "Animal Health"
I add a component with number "1" and type "Enhanced Content (1 can be added)"
I add "1" section of "Images" in component
I upload a file called "TestLogo.jpg" to component's "Images" section "1"
I add "1" section of "PDF / Coupon" in component
I upload a file called "Test.pdf" to component's "PDF / Coupon" section "1"
I have shown the side bar
I click Next on Product Configure page
I verify the current stage as "Propose"
I verify the Order Details
I verify the Sales Person
I select the billing account "THE ASCOT HOSPITAL & CLINICS LTD (510435041)" for customer "MercyAscot"
I set "Yellow Gold Listing" contract term as "10 months (Minimum*)"
I click reprice button of product "Yellow Gold Listing"
I verify the price calculation info of "Yellow Gold Listing"
I set "Yellow Gold Listing" payment option as "Monthly"
I click apply options to all button of product "Yellow Gold Listing"
I add art notes for current product "Art notes blah blah";
I add admin notes for current product "Admin notes .... ";
I verify the order total price
I save the current order
I verify the message "The order was saved."
I propose the current order
I verify the current stage as "Accept"
I verify the Order Details
I verify the Sales Person
I set the acceptance type as "Customer ECAP"
I upload an acceptance file "Test.pdf"
I accept this order
I verify the current stage as "Checkout and Complete"
I verify the check out summary price
I submit this order
I verify the order price in complete page
I click view order button
I select the order provisioning tab
There should be an "Animal Health" classification
The "Animal Health" should contain a "Yellow Gold Listing" order item
The "Animal Health" "Yellow Gold Listing" order item should not be complete
I click complete on the "Animal Health" "Yellow Gold Listing" order item
The "Animal Health" "Yellow Gold Listing" order item should be complete
The "Animal Health" should contain a "Enhanced Content" order item
The "Animal Health" "Enhanced Content" order item should not be complete
I click complete on the "Animal Health" "Enhanced Content" order item
The "Animal Health" "Enhanced Content" order item should be complete

elements.name: Open a existing customer and cancel the provisioning products.

steps.name: I click the customers menu option
I search for a customer called "MercyAscot"
I view the customer called "MercyAscot"
I click tab "Existing Products"
I search for a product "Gold Priority Listing" with filter "Equals"
I expand product section "Digital"
I cancel existing "Digital" products with following criteria:
I choose cancellation reason as "Cutting back on costs" for all
I propose the current order
I set the acceptance type as "Customer ECAP"
I upload an acceptance file "Test.pdf"
I accept this order
I submit this order
I click view order button
I select the order provisioning tab
